message.text:
Get to know JPMAP-FEU! ✨

The Junior People Management Association of the Philippines – FEU is more than just an organization — it’s a training ground for future leaders who value teamwork, integrity, and growth. Here, you’ll discover what people management truly means and how it can prepare you for both your academic and professional journey. 🌿

Be part of our community and start your journey with us! Apply now through this link:
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2

#JPMAPFEUChapter

#JPMAPapaibigKaSaIloilo

In almost every career, you will need to know how to work with, guide, and manage people -whether it's in small team, a department, or an entire company. In almost every career, you will need to know how to work with, guide, and manage people -whether it's in small team, a department, or an entire company. May be a graphic of map and text that says "Whatis is JDMAR The Junior People Management Association of the Philippines- FEU (JPMAP-FEU) is a student organization that helps members become future leaders by teaching them the basics of people management, or simply, how to work well with others and guide them toward shared goals. In almost every career, you will need to know how to work with, guide, and manage people -whether it's in small team, a department, or an entire company.
